question: 4 & 30 Nine or Ten x Rose
answer:
4: Assuming it is Ten x Rose, Rose would be working in a coffee shop straight after her “break up” with Jimmy Stone. She mostly does it for the money. Then, Ten, a recently orphaned, horribly traumatized, college student (or man depends on what age they would be.) starts frequenting the shop every day. They fight at first or she is totally enamoured by him. Something happens (Ten gets into a fight, media interfers, Jimmy Stone comes back, a bad anniversary or memory) and they are driven into each other’s arms. Typical trope chaos ensues with plenty of fluff, angst, love, friendship, kissing, etc…

30: since the previous one was Ten x Rose, I’ll make this one Nine x Rose. Rose Tyler and her mother just won tickets to a fantastic holiday resort. Probably snow in Christmas-y time. Nine, who has lost someone that truly matters to him a year ago around the time (family, lover, friend, etc…) comes to the resort because he had frequented it before with the person/people he lost. If we want to be cheesy, rooms get mixed up and Nine and Rose have to spend a night together. Or possibly, Rose could accidentally ram into him while taking their free ski lessons. They could get stuck together. Rose would be weary of his harsh, criticizing nature at first but then they slowly start to get to know each other and things get better from there.

(Sorry it is this long but I guess those are some of my favorite stories to see or write). Thank you for this fun ask!
